Long-term follow-up of advanced-stage low-grade lymphoma patients treated 
upfront with high-dose sequential chemotherapy and autograft.

Tarella C(1), Caracciolo D, Corradini P, Zallio F, Ladetto M, Cuttica A, Rossi 
G, Novero D, Gavarotti P, Pileri A.

Author information:
(1)Dipartimento di Medicina e Oncologia Sperimentale, Azienda Ospedaliera S 
