475. Anticancer Res. 2000 Jan-Feb;20(1B):573-7.

Significance of surgical resection for the treatment of multiple brain 
metastases.

Iwadate Y(1), Namba H, Yamaura A.

Author information:
(1)Department of Neurosurgery, Chiba University, School of Medicine, Japan. 
iwadate@med.m.chiba-u.ac.jp

BACKGROUND: We investigated the role of surgery in the treatment of multiple 
brain metastases when performed with radiation therapy.
